# 9 UJes’ U Yeza Futhi!

        Khalisan’ icilongo kakhulu;  uJes’ u yeza futhi;Bonke ba bhekisise phezulu uJes’ u yeza futhi    
CHORUS’Yeza futhi! Yeza futhi! uJes’ u yeza futhi!    
Memezani naseziqongweni, uJes’ u yeza futhi;Li za nobukhosi iZinyane, uJes’ u yeza futhi;    
Hlokomanini lwandle namaza, uJes’ u yeza futhi;Qubukani kanjalo zinhlanzi, uJes’ u yeza futhi;    
       Zi yasitshela iziboniso, uJes’ u yeza futhi;Nawo umoya u yavunguza, uJes’ u yeza futhi;    
       Izizwe zonke zi thukuthele, uJes’ u yeza futhi;Nalo ulwazi futhi lwandile, uJes’ u yeza futhi;
